content: krustevalexander: Contributed a new Imgflip plugin for generating memes through PR #2711 (+1070/-445 lines), followed by a refactoring PR #2846 to simplify and fix exports in the same feature (+32/-64 lines). Created and resolved issue #2432 related to a module loading problem. Activity was sporadic, with contributions on only 3 days this month, primarily focused on feature development and refactoring work across 21 modified files.
